STRIKE                                    rank 5   60 sp
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Strike is a multi-player spell.  It takes three monks to cast the Strike
spell.  In any order 3 monks use the command 'strike <target>'.  After the
third monk types the command the spell is unleashed, hurling fire down upon
the victim.  The spell costs 60 spell points per Monk and does massive damage
on the target.  The monster will attack the Monk who releases the spell
(the third caster)

